{"tid":1378832,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[正能撚] 不要說 撤啦咪送頭 試著說 我支持前線","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:29:48.000Z","uid":998,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f37e70470a0caf1d2e3f185ce6b2e412a69e874a","tid":1378832,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:46:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>前線無論做咩, 只要唔殺狗, 一律支持. 不分, 不割</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家好多P牌仔/5毛帶風向就係想分化前線同和理非, 等前線心灰意冷自我收皮<br />\n但我地要記住, 我地目標係一致. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">面對分化post, 不留cm, 不負皮, 不正皮, block, 上一頁 </span></span>, 就係咁簡單. 你比反應佢地就中計了<br />\n<br />\n記住粱天琦講過咩, 不要教條主義, 你覺得方向可行, 就去做, 唔好因為方向唔同就批評, 唔好因為被批評就動搖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我支持前線<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我屌你老母官鄉商黑"},{"pid":"feba2e703b6fbbb00755dbdb852108b932431bd7","tid":1378832,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:47:24.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"bf458c700bcb9e9f3ac25b1530c28d11fb004ece","tid":1378832,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:49:52.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"a1a5b8a8e9206b961893510b86399cc516ed9550","tid":1378832,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:52:29.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"1c4088d953df46e67f69baff134c917a22ff7834","tid":1378832,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:54:43.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"ecb240f7fbaf70945ccfa2551b4a87e37ec871a8","tid":1378832,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:58:18.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"d65470611864e6c3e58b5eff89e010e5974c3ed2","tid":1378832,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi